This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories, as it deals with optimizing image captioning systems using reinforcement learning. It also involves deep learning techniques, which are commonly studied in the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques, as it aims to improve the performance of image captioning systems by optimizing their output with respect to non-differentiable metrics.
